<table border="1" align="center" width="100%" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="border-left-color: #006aaf; border-bottom-color: #006aaf; border-top-color: #006aaf; border-collapse: collapse; border-right-color: #006aaf">
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td width="100%">
            <div id="customerLogo">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="font: 12px verdana" id="messagebody">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="font: 12px verdana" id="Signature">
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Hi, </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">I have an immediate requirement opening for an <span style="background: yellow">Oracle DBA position in Minneapolis, MN for 6+ month&rsquo;s contract</span>. I would appreciate if you could send your updated word format resume along with best contact details ASAP.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Here are the requirement details:</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="color: blue; font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Position &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Oracle DBA</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="color: blue; font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Location &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Minneapolis, MN</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="color: blue; font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Duration &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 6+ month&rsquo;s contract</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: red; font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Face-to-Face&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : May be required</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><u><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">DESCRIPTION:</font></span></u></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Client is seeking a Oracle DBA to come in and assist their existing DBA group for ~ 6 months. Production environment is very model centric so background in similar setups is ideal. In addition, candidates with strength in both DB modeling and working with application development teams has been key in the past.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><u><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">ROLE DETAILS:</font></span></u></strong></div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Collaborates with application development team(s) in the analysis of applications requirements, design and construction processes </font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Creates and maintains physical data models that meet the business and systems requirements</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Constructs and supports transactional, operational, and informational data stores in the development and testing environment. Manages changes to the application data model and generates DDL from the model.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Scripts changes into package to be promoted though the environment stack.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Develops and maintains stored procedures, database triggers, packages, and functions as required by the application design.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Manages users* accounts and roles in the development and testing environment.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Assists development teams with achieving optimal application performance.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Partners with developers and data analysts to develop test data for unit testing</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Copies or moves data from one database to another as required</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Partners with Operations DBA in applying database patches and upgrades to application databases, including coordination of testing, data conversion, and migrations as required</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Complies with the established company-wide database standards, best practices, SOPs and the governing directives of the Enterprise Data Architect.</font></span></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><u><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">SKILLS SPECIFICALLY REQUIRED:</font></span></u></strong></div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Oracle DBA. (5 years preferred)</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">DB Modeling Tools</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Data Modeling of OLTP and/or OLAP systems using ERD and/or UML modeling techniques</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">PL/SQL development and debugging</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Shell scripting.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Writing build/maintenance scripts that allow databases and their corresponding objects to be created/modified in different environments</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Monitoring and optimizing system performance using index tuning, disk optimization, and other methods</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Making tuning recommendations to developers related to PL/SQL</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Working in a multi-tier architecture in client/server environment</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Diagnosing and troubleshooting application and database issues</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Ability to operate in unstructured environment (assess, establish plan of action, execute)</font></span></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><u><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">NICE TO HAVE:</font></span></u></strong></div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">SQL, Transact SQL, PL/SQL development and debugging</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Making tuning recommendations to developers related to TSQL</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Sybase DBA (5 years)</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">SQL Server DBA (5 years)</font></span></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><a name="_MailAutoSig"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">Thanks/Regards,</font></span></a></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: green; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'"><font size="3">SAMEER</font></span><span style="color: navy; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">,</font></span><span style="color: navy; font-family: Cambria"><br>
            </span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">400 W Cummings Park,</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">Suite #<span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria"> 2850</span></font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">Woburn, MA-01801</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria">Email:</span><u><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: blue; font-family: Cambria">sameer@xperttech.com</span></u></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">Ph# 781-399-4354 | Fax # 781 207 0709 | </font></span><a href="http://www.xperttech.com/" title="blocked::http://www.xperttech.com/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">www.xperttech.com</font></span></a></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial"><font size="3">IMPORTANT NOTE</font></span><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial">: If you have received this email in error or prefer not to receive such emails in future, please reply with &quot;&quot;</span><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: red; font-family: Arial">Remove</span><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial">&quot;&quot; in the subject line and the email-id(s) to be removed. All removal requests will be honored ASAP.</span></font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: green; font-family: Webdings">P </span><font face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: green">Please consider the environment - do you really need to print this email?</span></font></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            </div>
